                     <interp inst="t17900915-73-person718" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am a constable: I took the prisoner into custody; I have the handkerchief; it was picked up when the prisoner dropped it; I saw it dropped, and saw it picked up.</p>
               <p>(Deposed to.)</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I was walking through Smithfield, and saw the handkerchief lying, and I picked it up; I have no witnesses.</p>
